description: CSOP ETF Series - CSOP SZSE ChiNext ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by CSOP Asset Management Limited. It invests in the public equity markets of China. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the stocks of large-cap and mid-cap companies. The fund seeks to replicate the performance of the ChiNext Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. CSOP ETF Series - CSOP SZSE ChiNext ETF was formed on May 13, 2015 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: CSOP SZSE ChiNext ETF
